From d03b191dbd1cbebdf0aecad3508f3abe66347a80 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Kingsley Wunzooya Nahyi <kingley.nahyi@ashesi.edu.gh>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 11:34:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add responsive breakpoints across main site and hub pages

- Added mobile/tablet media queries to 7 main-site pages (home, alumni,
  our-mission, our-partners, privacy-policy, this-is-aiesec) covering
  hero text scaling, grid collapses, and flex stacking
- Added sidebar-collapse responsive pattern to 18 hub pages, plus
  page-specific grid overrides for pages with extra image/video grids
- exchange-signup.html left unchanged (already uses clamp()/% widths)
